high_descs: Walk across the room to face the right side of the kitchen table.
Pick up the knife on the kitchen table.
Step to the right to face the apple on the kitchen table.
Cut the apple on the kitchen table into three pieces.
Look down to face the close edge of the kitchen table.
Place the knife on the edge of the kitchen table.
Look up to face the piece of apple on the kitchen table.
Pick up the piece of apple on the kitchen table.
Turn left and walk across the room to face the microwave.
Heat the piece of apple in the microwave and remove it.
Turn around and Walk across the room to face the right side of the kitchen table.
Place the piece of apple on the kitchen table.
anns.task_desc: To heat a piece of apple as well as place it on the kitchen table.

high_descs: Head across the room and walk around to the right side of the round black table.
Pick up the butterknife on the table.
Turn right to move over a few feet to face the table again.
Slice the yellow fruit on the table with the butterknife.
Turn left to move over a few feet to face the table once more.
Put the butterknife down on the round table.
Turn right to move over a few feet to face the table yet again.
Pick up a slice of the yellow fruit on the table.
Turn around and walk around the table to the opposite side of the room to the microwave.
Open the microwave to heat the fruit slice for a moment, then take the fruit slice back out and close the microwave.
Turn around and go back to the round black table where the butterknife is.
Set the fruit slice down on the table to the right of the butterknife.
anns.task_desc: Microwave a slice of yellow fruit and bring it back to the round black table.

high_descs: Go across the room, turn right, go the fridge, turn left and then turn around to the table.
Pick up the knife in the middle of the table.
Turn to the right and then turn back to the left.
Cut the apple on the table behind the lettuce.
Turn to the left and then turn back to the right toward the table.
Put the knife on top of the knife on the table.
Turn right and turn back left to the table.
Pick up a slice of apple on the table.
Turn left and go across the room to the microwave.
Put the apple in the microwave, cook it and pick it back up.
Turn around, head back to the table, turn right to the fridge, turn left and then turn right to the table.
Put the slice of apple on the table in front of the lettuce.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked slice of apple on the table.
